Game format

Conditions:
	- KEYBOARD_INPUT_REGEX
		* Value: regex to match input against
	- SECONDS_REMAINING
		* Value: seconds until end of game
	- CHECKPOINT_REACHED
		* Value: checkpoint reference

Actions:
	- UPDATE_TIME
	- PLAY_SOUND
	- STOP_SOUND
	- TURN_LIGHT_ON
	- TURN_LIGHT_OFF






